Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

nrow(mfifa)
## [1] 57793
ncol(mfifa)
## [1] 6
country <- select(mfifa, country_full) %>% unique %>% nrow
table(mfifa$confederation) %>% barplot(col = "blue")

mfifa %>% group_by(country_full) %>% 
        mutate(x=1:n()) %>%
        ggplot(aes(x=rank_date, y=rank,group=country_full, color=country_full)) + geom_line() + theme(legend.position="none") + scale_y_reverse()
